title: Small hole in the new level mesh
body:
Hey, was just wandering around when I saw this! It's a small hole in the 3D level mesh, and through it you can see absolutely nothing.

It's below the entrance to Red team's blue buff.

http://i.imgur.com/cHzJgni.png

replies.body: THERE'S A BREACH IN THE MATRIX
That freaked me out at first
I'm pretty sure that's normal. Can't say 4 sure doe
it's for the little squirrel things you see in the jungle.
